  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Instalação de nghttp2</title>

    <para>
      Instale <application>nghttp2</application> executando os seguintes comandos:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr     \
            --disable-static  \
            --enable-lib-only \
            --docdir=/usr/share/doc/nghttp2-&nghttp2-version; &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      The test suite needs CUnit, which is beyond the scope of BLFS.
    </para>

    <para>
      Agora, como o(a) usuário(a) <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

